# cardiffnlp/flan-t5-small-tweet-emoji

This is [google/flan-t5-small](https://huggingface.co/google/flan-t5-small) fine-tuned on [cardiffnlp/super_tweeteval (tweet_emoji)](https://huggingface.co/datasets/cardiffnlp/super_tweeteval).

### Usage

```python
from transformers import pipeline

pipe = pipeline('text2text-generation', model="cardiffnlp/flan-t5-small-tweet-emoji")
output = pipe("Louis Loudlinson is back with 16 and 18 secs ")
```
